00:02:58.360 --> 00:03:01.780
For example, think about
the problems we confront--

00:03:01.780 --> 00:03:05.140
chronic and infectious
diseases undermining the health

00:03:05.140 --> 00:03:09.880
of populations; natural
disasters strike, often

00:03:09.880 --> 00:03:13.720
