00:06:45.520 --> 00:06:48.010
DEEPAK CHOPRA: Well,
thank you, Dr. Williams--

00:06:48.010 --> 00:06:48.970
Dean Williams.

00:06:48.970 --> 00:06:51.385
And thank you all
