an experiment right now.

00:27:30.660 --> 00:27:31.900
We should take five seconds.

00:27:31.900 --> 00:27:32.733
Are you game for it?

00:27:32.733 --> 00:27:33.772
AUDIENCE: Yes.

00:27:33.772 --> 00:27:35.230
DEEPAK CHOPRA: Are
