00:27:50.450 --> 00:27:52.345
Are you aware right now?

00:27:52.345 --> 00:27:52.929
AUDIENCE: Yes.

00:27:52.929 --> 00:27:55.136
DEEPAK CHOPRA: Can you be
a little more enthusiastic?

00:27:55.136 --> 00:27:56.224
[LAUGHTER]

00:27:56.224 --> 00:27:58.047
Are you aware right now?

00:27:58.047 --> 00:27:59.180
AUDIENCE: Yes.

00:27:59.180 --> 00:28:00.730
DEEPAK CHOPRA:
