00:28:07.570 --> 00:28:09.610
So same question, and
then you can say yes

00:28:09.610 --> 00:28:11.410
when I left my hand up.

00:28:11.410 --> 00:28:12.025
Are you aware?

00:28:16.756 --> 00:28:18.167
AUDIENCE: Yes.

00:28:18.167 --> 00:28:20.000
DEEPAK CHOPRA: So are
you aware is a though.

00:28:20.000 --> 00:28:21.620
The answer is yes is a thought.

00:28:21.620 --> 00:28:24.740
In between is you as awareness.

00:28:24.740 --> 00:28:28.880
