their thoughts and perceptions

00:28:28.880 --> 00:28:31.730
and experiences in
the external world

00:28:31.730 --> 00:28:34.350
that they never get in
touch with themselves.

00:28:34.350 --> 00:28:37.990
So now, I'm going to ask you the
same question, are you aware?

00:28:37.990 --> 00:28:41.030
And this time, just be aware
of that, which is listening.

00:28:41.030 --> 00:28:41.900
Are you aware?

00:28:47.170 --> 00:28:51.670
This presence is who you really
are, not your thoughts, which

00:28:51.670 --> 00:28:58.820
recycle in social media, but
the presence in which experience

00:28:58.820 --> 00:28:59.950
occurs.

00:28:59.950 --> 00:29:04.530
You can stop anytime and
ask yourself, am I aware.

00:29:04.530 --> 00:29:07.090
Shouldn't be a
complicated process.

